{
  "title": "Qabas tu bunun",
  "titleCh": "祖先之聲",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "布農族人的歌謠有其功能和內容，大致上可分成祭儀禮讚之歌，生活寫照之歌謠，以及兒童歌謠。下面這首歌謠是卓群布農族人最能表現自我人生觀，以及自我解放之生活歌謠。",
      "ab": "Maca sintusauc is Bunun, nanu’ maiza ca sinpacqal tu iskama’az ca sintusauci’, maqtu’ pavazun minpiia ta’, maiza ca sintusauc is sinluluc’an, maiza ca sintusauc is iniqumican, maiza amin ca sintusauc is uvava’az. Maca sintusauc ha’an nastu’ dii tupa’un tu “Qabas tu bunun”. Cia ti’ ca madaduu sala ispacqal is iniqumicas Takitudu.",
